### Getting Started
Our Android library will help you manage the token with Omise API.

When creating token with library, it will prevent transmitting user card data via your environment. This library also allows you to securely store customers card data and can be used for their next payment with out input it again.

All sensitive data is transmitted via our PCI-DSS certified secure servers.

